<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">With only 1 mez spell (fascinate) at my level, I usually only mez 3 targets, sometimes 4.  More than that and I know I can't do the rounds without lapses.
<br />

<br />
Compared with EQ, the life expectancy of an enchanter in EQII is much longer.  Mobs don't beeline for me when mez is broken.  In EQ, I think enchanters had the most deaths per character.
<br />

<br />
Mez in EQII seems to be a slightly more powerful and less risky spell.
<br />

<br />

<br />

